CCR2D1Picture
=============
A format for encoding pictures for use in CCR2D1.

Header
------
{'C', 'C', 'R', '2', 'D', '1', 'P', '\x01'}

Properties
----------
{width << 24, width << 16, width <<  8, width,
height << 24, height<< 16, height<<  8, height}

Pixels
------
for each pixel
	{dnsty, color.length, color as ascii}


CCR2D1CompressedPicture
=======================
CCR2D1Ps might be compressed with GZip, but it's too much of a hassle
right now.
